<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạảj̊halu mā saẘfa yā̊̉tī fī ạl̊gẖadi ạảẘ baʿ̊dahu
 fāl̊gẖadu fī ʿil̊mi rabĩy laẙsa kẖāfiⁿ ʿin̊dahu
 laẙsa hamĩy mā yaṣīru min̊ ạủmūriⁿ ậtīāt̊
 hamĩy ạản̊ ạủr̊ḍīa rabĩy fī ạl̊ḥayāẗi wāl̊mamāt̊

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: las̊tu ạảd̊rī mā yakūnu min̊ ḥayātī fī ạl̊gẖadi
 ạảʿ̊lamu sẖaẙyaⁿ̉ạ yaqīnaⁿạ rabĩy mum̊sikuⁿ yadī

[V3]
 2- ạảʿ̊lamu: ạldãr̊bu munīru ạảʿ̊lamu: rabĩy ạảmīn̊
 fah̊wa lī kẖaẙru rafīqiⁿ wah̊wa lī kẖaẙru muʿīn̊
 ʿan̊ qarībiⁿ saẘfa ạảm̊ḍī ại̹lay̱ maẘṭini ạl̊kẖulūd̊
 ḥaẙtẖu lạ ạldãm̊ʿu yasīlu lạ walạ ạl̊maẘtu yasūd̊

[V4]
 3- ạ̉jhl ạlmstqblạt ạ̉jhl mạ sykwn
 ạ̹nmạ ạ̉ʿlm ạ̉n sydy ạ̉b ḥnwn
 fhw yʿny bạlṭywr wkdẖạ by yʿtny
 dmh ykfyny strạ rwḥh ymlạ̉ny</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉jhl mạ swf yạ̉ty</title>
